   OEM restrictions harmed consumers who preferred Windows with Navigator
   or with no browser at all, harmed the OEMs who wanted to serve the
   "[m]any consumers [who] desire to separate their choice of a Web
   browser from their choice of an operating system," an 30 d "stifled 28
